{
  "stem": "21482.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Barracks were, you know, freezing cold in wintertime.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a stove in the middle, never really could warm the whole place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, everybody was so petrified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were so afraid of what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the next day, some of those people who work for Oskar Schindler or went to work for Madritsch, those were the people who were able to smuggle their children, that had already made arrangement with their Polish friends and smuggled the children and gave them to the Polish people, their friends who would-- that to agree to help them, to take care, to save their children.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a group from the camp that went to clean up the ghetto that day, the first day of camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first day in the camp, you know, it was the first time men and women were separated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The barracks were men barracks, women barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a bathhouse, there was a latrine, there was a kitchen, and there was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's like a clinic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the workshops were up on a hill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And up on a hill was the villa of Amon Goth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the middle was this huge appellplatz, were like a huge meadow where everybody had to gather every morning and every night and be counted, make sure nobody escaped.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were counted by the Jewish police, by the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Ukrainians actually volunteered to guard, to be guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, of course, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they went, reported to Amon Goth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Amon Goth would, you know, he would stand on that appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
